('urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1',2,56,56,'  And when he had called them together, he contrived a cunning plan, and said:'),
('urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1',2,56,57,' \"Hearken, my friends, a Dream from heaven came to me in my sleep through the ambrosial night, and most like was it to goodly Nestor, in form and in stature and in build.'),
('urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1',2,57,58,' \"Hearken, my friends, a Dream from heaven came to me in my sleep through the ambrosial night, and most like was it to goodly Nestor, in form and in stature and in build.'),
