('urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1',2,142,143,'  And the gathering was stirred like the long sea-waves of the Icarian main,  which the East Wind or the South Wind has raised, rushing upon them from the clouds of father Zeus.'),
